show.description: Anna becomes CEO Ian’s secret lover to save her boyfriend, Louis, but is abandoned by Ian and later dates playboy David. After being forced into marriage with crime lord Domenico, Anna is kidnapped, prompting Ian and Louis to team up and rescue her. Amid dark secrets and intense rivalries, Anna must choose between four men to find true love.
